         <div type="translation" xml:lang="fra" source="bib:Finot1920_01">
 	<p rend="stanza" n="1">De l'octogénaire Bhoja, qui érigea ici le <foreign>liṅga</foreign>, les dents tombées de sa bouche ont été déposées à la base de <foreign>triśūla</foreign>.</p>
         </div>
           <div type="translation" resp="part:argr part:kuch">
              <p rend="stanza" n="1">Of Bhoja, the eighty-year-old installer of the liṅga here, the canine teeth which had fallen from his mouth were placed at the base of the trident.</p>
           </div>
